entries.femaleVariant: So you two're gettin' along fine?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="さあ… どうかな… よくわからない…" t="I... I guess so... I don't even know..." b="" a=""/>
Too ordinary for you, huh? Gettin' bored already?
So what's his deal? Not enough of an asshole, violent drunk, gaslighting psycho, or--
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="何よ、あたしがおかしいって言いたいの？" t="Maybe I'm a psycho too, huh?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="だからロクな男ができない。そういうこと？" t="Maybe I just get what I deserve, is that it?" b="" a=""/>
Hey, cut that shit out. I didn't mean to...
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ただでさえ最悪な日だったのに、あんたまでそういうこと言うなんて！" t="It's not enough I had a bad day, now YOU have to get on my ass?!" b="" a=""/>
What happened? You wanna talk about it?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="うん… じゃあコーヒーでも飲みに行きましょ…" t="Yeah... let's go get a coffee or something..." b="" a=""/>
